>
>What size are the bolts that hold that [front floor] pan on to the 
>bus? I have the pan but the bolts are MIA?

They have 10mm heads and on my '64 they are a mix of machine thread
and sheet-metal thread.  The parts manual 
http://wow.atlasta.net/~mriluvu/oacdp/5867part.html (p. 341 and p. 345) 
says M6x10 for the machine thread and B6.3x13 for the sheet-metal thread.
Each has a washer.

Matt Roberds


